# Sports Layout System

All sports card layouts use a **2-column CSS grid** that keeps competitors
and market data aligned across the market header and every event row.

## Shared grid (MarketHeader + EventRow)

```
grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-3 pl-1.5
```

| Column | Content | Key classes |
|--------|---------|-------------|
| Col 1 | Competitors / CTA | `col-span-1`, competitors wrap in `max-w-xs w-full flex flex-col gap-y-1` |
| Col 2 | Market data / Outcome headers | `col-span-1 flex gap-x-1 text-center items-center` |

## MarketHeader (MarketHeaderV2)

- Background: gradient using `color-mix(in oklch, var(--color-cb-surface-3) …)`
- Borders: `0.5px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--color-cb-surface-3) 50%, transparent)` top and bottom
- Height: `min-h-8`
- Col 2 outcome labels: `flex-1 flex w-full items-center justify-center truncate`, text `text-[11px] font-medium`
- Market switcher (when >1 group): pill button with `border-2 border-cb-border rounded-full text-xs font-medium`

## EventRow (MatchupWrapper)

Structure inside the grid:

```
<div class="relative cursor-pointer group">
  <!-- absolute hover state layer -->
  <div class="flex flex-col p-2 gap-y-2 relative">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-3 pl-1.5">
      <!-- col-1: competitors -->
      <!-- col-2: odds -->
    </div>
    <!-- status row below the grid -->
  </div>
</div>
```

- Hover: absolute gradient layer `linear-gradient(to right, surface-4, surface-3, surface-2)`
- Divider between events: `GradientDivider` — `h-0.5` gradient from transparent → cb-border → transparent

## Market data column (OddsListContainer)

The outer container for odds inside col-2:

```
flex-1 flex justify-center gap-x-1
```

Each individual button wrapper:

```
w-full flex-1 flex justify-center
```

## OddsButton (OddsButtonV3 / OddsButtonUI)

Sizing and shape:

```
w-full h-full min-h-11 rounded-xl border
py-1 px-0.5
```

States:
- Default: `border-transparent`
- Selected: `border-cb-primary`
- Hover: `bg-cb-primary/[0.08]`
- Active: `bg-cb-primary/[0.16]`
- Suspended: Lock icon `size-[18px] text-cb-foreground-disabled`
- Closed (post-match): empty `min-h-11` div — **no icon, no text**

Inner layout:

```
mx-auto → flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-medium gap-x-1
```

Odds value: `h-7 p-0.5 relative flex items-center justify-center` with text `text-sm font-medium text-cb-accent`

### OddsButton label rule

**Never repeat in the button what the market header already shows.**

- The `label` prop on `OddsButton` is for line text that is *not* shown in the header (e.g. handicap lines like "-4.5", totals like "O/U 221.5").
- When the market header already shows outcome labels (1 / X / 2, Over / Under, 1 / 2), omit `label` from the button entirely — the odds value alone is sufficient.
- Market header outcome labels for head-to-head markets: always use **"1" / "2"** (not "Home" / "Away", not team abbreviations).

## MarketSwitcher button

Default state: `border-transparent` (no visible border). Hover: `border-cb-border`. Open: `border-cb-primary/60 bg-cb-primary/[0.08]`.

## CompetitorRow

```
flex items-center gap-x-3
```

- Icon: `size-5 rounded-full bg-cb-surface-4`
- Name: `text-xs font-bold truncate text-cb-foreground`
- Score: `text-xs font-bold text-cb-foreground tabular-nums`
- Winner indicator: SVG polygon `w-1.5 h-2`
- Loser dim: `opacity-40`

## Card container

```
rounded-[var(--cb-radius-lg)] bg-cb-surface-2 overflow-hidden
```

Header: `flex items-center gap-x-3 p-2.5`
Collapse toggle: `size-8 rounded-xl` with `bg-cb-surface-1` (open) / `bg-cb-surface-3` (closed)
Hover/active: `hover:bg-cb-foreground-muted/[0.08] active:bg-cb-foreground-muted/[0.16]`
